00:48:16.800 --> 00:48:19.310
crying all around, and that

00:48:19.320 --> 00:48:22.710
devil was blocking and causing havoc

00:48:22.720 --> 00:48:24.870
on the road to glory so people would

00:48:24.880 --> 00:48:27.270
be derailed.

00:48:27.280 --> 00:48:30.430
Does this make sense, what I'm saying?

00:48:30.440 --> 00:48:32.950
They would be derailed off of what God's

00:48:32.960 --> 00:48:36.230
original assignment was for you to do.

00:48:36.240 --> 00:48:37.990
God doesn't give you a second assignment

00:48:38.000 --> 00:48:40.710
until you finish the first assignment.

00:48:40.720 --> 00:48:42.830
Go back to what God originally told you

00:48:42.840 --> 00:48:44.190
to do.

00:48:44.200 --> 00:48:45.310
You say, 'Well, he hasn't told me to do

00:48:45.320 --> 00:48:46.750
anything else,'because you haven't been

00:48:46.760 --> 00:48:48.150
obedient with the first thing he told

00:48:48.160 --> 00:48:51.990
you to do. Obey what he told you to do,

00:48:52.000 --> 00:48:53.910
and you'll get

00:48:53.920 --> 00:48:57.950
letter B. It's like A, B, C, D; but

00:48:57.960 --> 00:49:01.670
you can't go from A to B to C to D until

00:49:01.680 --> 00:49:05.150
you've been obedient with A.

00:49:05.160 --> 00:49:08.270
There's an order

00:49:08.280 --> 00:49:10.790
all the way to

00:49:10.790 --> 00:49:10.800
XYZ.

00:49:10.800 --> 00:49:13.070
The alphabet is

00:49:13.080 --> 00:49:14.470
the way it is,

00:49:14.480 --> 00:49:16.550
but it's just an illustration.

00:49:18.720 --> 00:49:20.470
Mathematics would probably be better to do it

00:49:20.480 --> 00:49:22.390
like that.

00:49:22.400 --> 00:49:23.910
You have to

00:49:23.920 --> 00:49:25.750
learn addition, subtraction,

00:49:25.760 --> 00:49:27.590
multiplication,

00:49:27.590 --> 00:49:27.600
and

00:49:27.600 --> 00:49:28.790
division to get

00:49:28.790 --> 00:49:28.800
to algebra.

00:49:28.800 --> 00:49:30.390
You don't just start

00:49:30.400 --> 00:49:31.910
algebra until you learn the basics of

00:49:31.920 --> 00:49:33.870
everything else. The point is that

00:49:33.880 --> 00:49:36.790
people think, 'Why am I still dwarfed in

00:49:36.800 --> 00:49:39.510
my belief? Why am I still dwarfed in my

00:49:39.520 --> 00:49:42.470
faith? Why have I not grown

00:49:42.470 --> 00:49:42.480
up?'Because

00:49:42.480 --> 00:49:46.390
a plant does not grow

00:49:46.390 --> 00:49:46.400
well

00:49:46.400 --> 00:49:48.470
unless it's in the soil God planted you

00:49:48.480 --> 00:49:51.910
in. I cannot put a palm tree in

00:49:51.920 --> 00:49:55.590
Nebraska

00:49:55.600 --> 00:49:57.910
because God didn't design a palm tree to

00:49:57.920 --> 00:50:00.070
grow in Colorado

00:50:00.080 --> 00:50:02.230
or Nebraska. He designed it to be in

00:50:02.240 --> 00:50:03.470
Miami,

00:50:03.470 --> 00:50:03.480
Florida,

00:50:03.480 --> 00:50:08.070
or

00:50:08.080 --> 00:50:10.270
wherever.

00:50:10.280 --> 00:50:12.830
Do you understand? I cannot expect a

00:50:12.840 --> 00:50:14.470
beautiful

00:50:14.480 --> 00:50:16.230
evergreen cedar tree

00:50:16.240 --> 00:50:19.870
to grow on the beach.

00:50:19.880 --> 00:50:23.270
It doesn't work that way.

00:50:23.280 --> 00:50:24.390
And so God

00:50:24.400 --> 00:50:27.710
has a specific place for you to be

00:50:27.720 --> 00:50:30.710
so that you grow your fruit

00:50:30.720 --> 00:50:33.350
and you grow your tree. your life,

00:50:33.360 --> 00:50:34.950
your spiritual life, and I put you in this

00:50:34.960 --> 00:50:37.150
place. But you are a baby, and a baby

00:50:37.150 --> 00:50:37.160
doesn't

00:50:37.160 --> 00:50:38.150
know where it's supposed to be.

00:50:38.160 --> 00:50:40.150
A baby just needs to yield.

00:50:40.160 --> 00:50:41.550
I just go, "It's okay, honey. I'll

00:50:41.560 --> 00:50:43.550
help you."And he's gracious and

00:50:43.560 --> 00:50:45.270
merciful.

00:50:45.280 --> 00:50:47.350
But as I saw all these babies at the

00:50:47.360 --> 00:50:48.550
feet,

00:50:48.550 --> 00:50:48.560
the

00:50:48.560 --> 00:50:51.310
devil was laughing about it

00:50:51.310 --> 00:50:51.320
because

00:50:51.320 --> 00:50:53.030
he felt like he had the upper

00:50:53.040 --> 00:50:54.510
hand.

00:50:54.520 --> 00:50:56.510
"See, I've blocked them from getting to

00:50:56.520 --> 00:50:57.950
where they're supposed to

00:50:57.950 --> 00:50:57.960
be."He

00:50:57.960 --> 00:50:59.990
was doing everything he could.

00:51:00.000 --> 00:51:03.270
As I was praying

00:51:03.280 --> 00:51:05.310
from the throne,

00:51:05.320 --> 00:51:08.590
I saw a shaft of light pierce that

00:51:08.600 --> 00:51:11.670
demonic spirit that looked almost

00:51:11.680 --> 00:51:13.790
like a bullet wound.

00:51:13.800 --> 00:51:15.910
And the glory of the Lord started to

00:51:15.920 --> 00:51:17.750
penetrate that demonic spirit, and it

00:51:17.760 --> 00:51:19.710
started to spread.

00:51:19.720 --> 00:51:23.630
The light started to disintegrate

00:51:23.640 --> 00:51:25.790
the center of this demonic being's

00:51:25.800 --> 00:51:27.750
chest

00:51:27.760 --> 00:51:29.350
by prayer,

00:51:29.360 --> 00:51:31.270
by the warriors,

00:51:31.280 --> 00:51:33.550
and all of a sudden

00:51:33.560 --> 00:51:37.230
that demonic spirit started to weaken.

00:51:37.240 --> 00:51:39.790
And the dark form of great black, which

00:51:39.800 --> 00:51:40.670
was—here's

00:51:40.680 --> 00:51:42.150
a color chart. Braden always was

00:51:42.160 --> 00:51:44.710
using this. This dark color,

00:51:44.720 --> 00:51:47.630
it was as black as molasses, the

00:51:47.630 --> 00:51:47.640
darkest

00:51:47.640 --> 00:51:50.110
black you could see, became a little

00:51:50.120 --> 00:51:51.550
gray,

00:51:51.550 --> 00:51:51.560
then

00:51:51.560 --> 00:51:54.430
became a little grayer, and his skin,

00:51:54.440 --> 00:51:56.590
whatever you want to call it, started to

00:51:56.600 --> 00:51:59.390
be see-through.

00:51:59.400 --> 00:52:02.030
The babies that were on the ground

00:52:02.040 --> 00:52:03.590
started going back to where they were

00:52:03.600 --> 00:52:06.150
supposed to go.

00:52:06.160 --> 00:52:11.470
And I saw an adding of a supply

00:52:11.480 --> 00:52:15.790
of unoffended, repentant Christians that

00:52:15.800 --> 00:52:17.990
said, "I sell out to the Lord. I'm

00:52:18.000 --> 00:52:19.870
sorry I missed

00:52:19.870 --> 00:52:19.880
it,"and

00:52:19.880 --> 00:52:21.670
got back on the right path to go to

00:52:21.680 --> 00:52:23.230
the glory.

00:52:23.240 --> 00:52:25.030
And they put themselves where God had

00:52:25.040 --> 00:52:26.710
originally put them.

00:52:26.720 --> 00:52:28.110
They went back to where they were

00:52:28.120 --> 00:52:30.310
supposed to be. And they dealt with the

00:52:30.320 --> 00:52:32.230
offense. They dealt with the hurt. They

00:52:32.240 --> 00:52:34.070
dealt with the ego. They dealt with the

00:52:34.080 --> 00:52:36.630
pride. And they said, "Father, I yield

00:52:36.640 --> 00:52:38.070
to you. I'm going back to what you

00:52:38.080 --> 00:52:40.990
called me to do.

00:52:41.000 --> 00:52:43.630
Not my will, but yours be

00:52:43.630 --> 00:52:43.640
done."Because

00:52:43.640 --> 00:52:46.070
the willing and obedient will

00:52:46.080 --> 00:52:49.430
eat the good of the land.

00:52:49.440 --> 00:52:51.070
You say, "I don't understand why

00:52:51.080 --> 00:52:52.830
I'm not eating the good of the land,

00:52:52.840 --> 00:52:54.110
Brandon.

00:52:54.120 --> 00:52:56.790
Why are my finances struggling so bad?

00:52:56.800 --> 00:52:58.870
Why is all this?"Because you weren't willing

00:52:58.880 --> 00:53:00.430
and you weren't obedient to what God had

00:53:00.440 --> 00:53:01.870
told you to do.

00:53:01.880 --> 00:53:06.230
Go back to what God has told you to do.

00:53:06.240 --> 00:53:08.470
You say, "Well, I have all this. I felt

00:53:08.480 --> 00:53:10.030
like I was always called to the ministry.

00:53:10.040 --> 00:53:11.830
I felt like I was called to women's

00:53:11.840 --> 00:53:13.750
ministry. I felt like I was going to do

00:53:13.760 --> 00:53:16.350
this, and I never saw

00:53:16.350 --> 00:53:16.360
the

00:53:16.360 --> 00:53:19.150
full manifestation of it because you

00:53:19.160 --> 00:53:21.190
derailed yourself because you didn't

00:53:21.200 --> 00:53:23.950
stay on what God had told you to

00:53:23.950 --> 00:53:23.960
do."Go

00:53:23.960 --> 00:53:28.310
back to the ABCs and 123s to learn to

00:53:28.320 --> 00:53:31.430
get to algebra.

00:53:31.440 --> 00:53:32.630
"Well, I'm big enough. I don't need all

00:53:32.630 --> 00:53:32.640
that."No,

00:53:32.640 --> 00:53:34.790
no, no. If you don't know

00:53:34.800 --> 00:53:36.790
your addition and your multiplication

00:53:36.800 --> 00:53:38.710
and all this, you'll never understand

00:53:38.720 --> 00:53:40.670
algebra. I don't care. "Well, you know

00:53:40.680 --> 00:53:42.190
what? I think I can solve

00:53:42.190 --> 00:53:42.200
it."You're

00:53:42.200 --> 00:53:44.590
never going to solve it.

00:53:44.600 --> 00:53:47.390
You're never going to solve algebra.

00:53:47.400 --> 00:53:49.190
You have to go back to what God had

00:53:49.200 --> 00:53:51.350
called you to do.

00:53:51.360 --> 00:53:54.030
Don't dwarf your roots. A tree that's

00:53:54.040 --> 00:53:56.190
planted in the wrong soil and plucked up

00:53:56.200 --> 00:53:58.910
so many times

00:53:58.920 --> 00:54:01.710
never develops like it should. The

00:54:01.720 --> 00:54:02.990
taproot

00:54:03.000 --> 00:54:05.110
goes down deep.

00:54:05.120 --> 00:54:06.750
And if you keep messing and pulling the

00:54:06.760 --> 00:54:09.150
taproot and doing all the things,

00:54:09.160 --> 00:54:11.510
you'll never become what God originally

00:54:11.520 --> 00:54:13.350
told you you would be

00:54:13.360 --> 00:54:14.790
because you haven't been obedient with

00:54:14.800 --> 00:54:16.150
what he asked you to do in the first

00:54:16.160 --> 00:54:17.910
place.

00:54:17.920 --> 00:54:20.390
And as I saw that devil start to

00:54:20.400 --> 00:54:22.190
disintegrate through prayer and

00:54:22.200 --> 00:54:23.910
intercession,

00:54:23.920 --> 00:54:26.710
I saw his parting of it. But I saw

00:54:26.720 --> 00:54:29.390
what was a blinder on those babies

00:54:29.400 --> 00:54:30.830
start going and bringing the babies

00:54:30.840 --> 00:54:32.430
back.

00:54:32.440 --> 00:54:34.230
And it goes with what the Lord said, "Be

00:54:34.240 --> 00:54:36.070
patient with my babies,

00:54:36.080 --> 00:54:38.910
for you were once a baby.

00:54:38.920 --> 00:54:40.390
Be patient with the ones that are coming

00:54:40.400 --> 00:54:43.870
in, for you were once a

00:54:43.870 --> 00:54:43.880
baby."There

00:54:43.880 --> 00:54:45.350
was more to the vision. It was

00:54:45.360 --> 00:54:46.710
about some things the Lord was showing

00:54:46.720 --> 00:54:48.390
me privately. I won't bring all that

00:54:48.390 --> 00:54:48.400
because

00:54:48.400 --> 00:54:50.030
you'll say I'm bragging.

00:54:50.040 --> 00:54:52.150
But the Lord said to me

00:54:52.160 --> 00:54:54.710
specifically some things directly to

00:54:54.720 --> 00:54:57.070
Diana and I in that. And it was

00:54:57.080 --> 00:54:58.550
really encouraging.

00:54:58.560 --> 00:55:03.110
But I want to say to you,

00:55:04.080 --> 00:55:07.190
don't be

00:55:07.200 --> 00:55:09.910
offended. Go back to, like I told you, the

00:55:09.910 --> 00:55:09.920
Bait of

00:55:09.920 --> 00:55:12.310
Satan.

00:55:12.320 --> 00:55:14.950
The devil will use all these things

00:55:14.960 --> 00:55:17.150
against you to derail what God has

00:55:17.160 --> 00:55:21.590
called you to do because of your flesh.

00:55:23.480 --> 00:55:25.390
I'm just trying to help.

00:55:25.400 --> 00:55:27.950
And as I saw that,

00:55:27.960 --> 00:55:29.350
I saw

00:55:29.360 --> 00:55:31.750
churches starting to explode

00:55:31.760 --> 00:55:33.510
because people say, "I'm not going back.

00:55:33.520 --> 00:55:35.230
I'll just watch online.

00:55:35.240 --> 00:55:37.230
I'm going to do this. They did this to

00:55:37.240 --> 00:55:38.870
me. I'm upset; I'm not ever going to

00:55:38.880 --> 00:55:42.510
step foot back into a church

00:55:42.510 --> 00:55:42.520
again."Bunch

00:55:42.520 --> 00:55:44.790
of hypocrites. I'm

00:55:44.800 --> 00:55:46.350
telling you, we're all saved by grace. We

00:55:46.360 --> 00:55:48.230
all have something we're overcoming. There

00:55:48.230 --> 00:55:48.240
isn't

00:55:48.240 --> 00:55:49.670
one of us better than the

00:55:49.680 --> 00:55:50.510
other.

00:55:50.520 --> 00:55:52.310
I don't care who you are.

00:55:52.320 --> 00:55:53.870
You could be the

00:55:53.880 --> 00:55:56.110
one that would be closest to

00:55:56.120 --> 00:55:58.070
Peter walking on the water.

00:55:58.080 --> 00:55:59.910
But you still have issues because Peter

00:55:59.920 --> 00:56:02.710
denied him. I want you to understand

00:56:02.720 --> 00:56:04.470
that all of us have sinned and fallen

00:56:04.480 --> 00:56:06.550
short of the

00:56:06.550 --> 00:56:06.560
glory—all

00:56:06.560 --> 00:56:08.110
of us,

00:56:08.120 --> 00:56:10.950
even Peter.

00:56:10.960 --> 00:56:13.670
And Peter was awesome,

00:56:13.680 --> 00:56:14.950
obviously.

00:56:14.960 --> 00:56:16.630
I mean, seriously, he was walking on the

00:56:16.640 --> 00:56:18.070
water.

00:56:18.080 --> 00:56:19.990
I mean, he was cool.

00:56:20.000 --> 00:56:21.350
I want to be cool; I

00:56:21.360 --> 00:56:23.190
want to be buddies with him. Well, let's watch

00:56:23.200 --> 00:56:25.670
him walk on the water, you know?

00:56:25.680 --> 00:56:30.510
But the same man denied him,

00:56:30.510 --> 00:56:30.520
and

00:56:30.520 --> 00:56:32.830
Jesus forgave him.

00:56:32.840 --> 00:56:34.790
So even

00:56:34.800 --> 00:56:36.670
on our best day,

00:56:36.680 --> 00:56:38.430
you know,

00:56:38.440 --> 00:56:40.070
we're all just sick sinners saved by

00:56:40.080 --> 00:56:41.310
grace.

00:56:41.320 --> 00:56:43.030
Thank God for his blood, ladies and

00:56:43.040 --> 00:56:45.270
gentlemen. But I'm trying to tell you,

00:56:45.280 --> 00:56:47.390
there's coming a revival. There's coming

00:56:47.400 --> 00:56:49.630
a shaking. And you bring a piece to that

00:56:49.640 --> 00:56:51.470
church. You bring a piece to where you

00:56:51.480 --> 00:56:53.630
were supposed to be that nobody else is

00:56:53.640 --> 00:56:55.310
going to fulfill because he assigned you

00:56:55.320 --> 00:56:57.150
to be there.

00:56:57.160 --> 00:56:58.790
He may bring somebody else along that

00:56:58.800 --> 00:57:01.430
has something similar, maybe

00:57:01.440 --> 00:57:03.550
because you might be that

00:57:03.560 --> 00:57:06.390
hard-headed. But the bottom line is that

00:57:06.400 --> 00:57:08.710
you have what it takes. You have that

00:57:08.720 --> 00:57:12.510
gift. You have that puzzle piece.

00:57:12.520 --> 00:57:14.790
And that puzzle piece, you were made to

00:57:14.800 --> 00:57:17.030
fit that perfect puzzle.

00:57:17.040 --> 00:57:19.470
Because of you, you make a whole

00:57:19.480 --> 00:57:21.390
picture.

00:57:21.400 --> 00:57:23.710
And they go, 'You know what? Without

00:57:23.720 --> 00:57:25.590
that centerpiece, that whole thing would

00:57:25.600 --> 00:57:27.870
have been messed up. But thank God you

00:57:27.880 --> 00:57:30.550
came

00:57:30.550 --> 00:57:30.560
back.'So

00:57:30.560 --> 00:57:33.270
I just encourage you: seek your heart

00:57:33.280 --> 00:57:35.710
and where God wants you today.

00:57:35.720 --> 00:57:38.470
Ask the Father, 'Forgive me. Help

00:57:38.470 --> 00:57:38.480
me.'If

00:57:38.480 --> 00:57:40.870
I need to go

00:57:40.880 --> 00:57:43.030
back and make things right, if I need to

00:57:43.040 --> 00:57:45.350
do this, Father, search me

00:57:45.360 --> 00:57:48.150
and know me. It may be that

00:57:48.160 --> 00:57:51.150
God moved you on. Maybe, I don't

00:57:51.160 --> 00:57:52.150
know.

00:57:52.160 --> 00:57:55.990
But always inquire of the Lord. There

00:57:55.990 --> 00:57:56.000
have

00:57:56.000 --> 00:57:57.430
been a lot of big decisions that

00:57:57.440 --> 00:57:59.670
I've had to make in the last 48 hours.

00:57:59.680 --> 00:58:01.950
And the major thing that Diana, my

00:58:01.960 --> 00:58:05.710
wife, always said to me:

00:58:05.720 --> 00:58:09.310
'Brandon, have you inquired of the Lord?

00:58:09.320 --> 00:58:11.830
Have you sat and made the decisions

00:58:11.840 --> 00:58:13.470
based on

00:58:13.480 --> 00:58:16.550
him or out of just what you think or

00:58:18.950 --> 00:58:18.960
fear?'Did

00:58:21.040 --> 00:58:24.350
you inquire of the Lord?

00:58:24.360 --> 00:58:26.510
Did you fast and pray before you

00:58:26.520 --> 00:58:28.990
make major decisions today? And I

00:58:28.990 --> 00:58:29.000
say,

00:58:29.000 --> 00:58:30.830
'Yeah, I need

00:58:30.830 --> 00:58:30.840
to.'So

00:58:30.840 --> 00:58:33.070
I did today. I did Sunday. I

00:58:33.080 --> 00:58:34.190
prayed.

00:58:34.200 --> 00:58:36.270
And so it's amazing when you take that

00:58:36.280 --> 00:58:38.470
time.

00:58:38.480 --> 00:58:40.350
And there was this dear sister—and I'm

00:58:40.360 --> 00:58:42.030
not promoting her channel because I don't

00:58:42.040 --> 00:58:43.990
know what else she said—but the Lord

00:58:44.000 --> 00:58:46.070
said, 'I want you to go and listen to

00:58:46.070 --> 00:58:46.080
this lady.'She

00:58:46.080 --> 00:58:48.150
was a witch

00:58:48.160 --> 00:58:49.950
and she got born again,

00:58:49.960 --> 00:58:52.310
and her channel was about hexes and

00:58:52.320 --> 00:58:54.150
vexes,

00:58:54.160 --> 00:58:57.190
talking about the occult coming against

00:58:57.200 --> 00:58:58.790
Christians and the symptoms and

00:58:58.800 --> 00:59:00.670
things like that. And she said, "I

00:59:00.680 --> 00:59:03.670
got born again. I was in the occult, and

00:59:03.680 --> 00:59:05.150
she was talking about the blood of Jesus

00:59:05.160 --> 00:59:06.790
and all these things, but I'm very

00:59:06.800 --> 00:59:08.870
